============================================================
PHASE 23 OBJECTIVE
============================================================

Build the Sovereign Enterprise Control Plane for zDash.

Main goals:

1. Add global governance policy engine
2. Add AI agent permission governance
3. Add cross-module safety enforcement
4. Add compliance evidence collector
5. Add immutable audit export bundle
6. Add disaster recovery orchestration
7. Add backup verification and restore drills
8. Add incident command center
9. Add operational risk register
10. Add enterprise policy simulator
11. Add autonomous ops runbook executor in dry-run mode
12. Add control-plane dashboard pages
13. Add governance APIs
14. Add disaster recovery APIs
15. Add compliance APIs
16. Add full tests

Critical safety rule:
This phase must make the system safer, more auditable, and more recoverable.
It must not enable live trading, real IoT actions, real social posting, secret access, or unsafe automation by default.

