============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update `.env.example`:

GOVERNANCE_ENABLED=true
POLICY_ENGINE_ENABLED=true
POLICY_FAIL_CLOSED=true
POLICY_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true

AGENT_GOVERNANCE_ENABLED=true
AGENT_DEFAULT_PERMISSION_MODE=deny
AGENT_REQUIRE_EXPLICIT_GRANTS=true

SAFETY_ENFORCER_ENABLED=true
SAFETY_BLOCK_LIVE_TRADING=true
SAFETY_BLOCK_REAL_IOT=true
SAFETY_BLOCK_REAL_SOCIAL_POSTING=true
SAFETY_BLOCK_SECRET_EXPORT=true
SAFETY_BLOCK_UNREVIEWED_PLUGINS=true

COMPLIANCE_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_EVIDENCE_COLLECTION=true
COMPLIANCE_EXPORT_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_EXPORT_INCLUDE_SECRETS=false

DISASTER_RECOVERY_ENABLED=true
BACKUP_VERIFICATION_ENABLED=true
RESTORE_DRILL_DRY_RUN=true
RECOVERY_POINT_OBJECTIVE_MINUTES=60
RECOVERY_TIME_OBJECTIVE_MINUTES=120

INCIDENT_COMMAND_ENABLED=true
RUNBOOK_EXECUTOR_ENABLED=true
RUNBOOK_EXECUTOR_DRY_RUN=true
RISK_REGISTER_ENABLED=true

Rules:

- Fail closed when policy engine is unavailable.
- Agent default permission mode must be deny.
- Live trading must remain blocked by default.
- Real IoT must remain blocked by default.
- Real social posting must remain blocked by default.
- Secret export must remain blocked by default.
- Runbook executor must default to dry-run.
- Restore drills must default to dry-run.

