- register_backup(record)
- verify_backup(backup_id)
- run_restore_drill(backup_id, dry_run=true)
- generate_recovery_plan()
- get_readiness_score()

Rules:
- Restore drill is dry-run by default.
- Real restore must require admin and typed confirmation:
  CONFIRM_RESTORE
- Do not overwrite live data by default.
- Verification must calculate checksum where possible.
- Recovery readiness score must include:
  - recent verified backup
  - restore drill success
  - RPO/RTO config
  - incident runbook availability
  - audit export availability

